Business-OnlinePayment-Litle

A plugin for the Business::OnlinePayment interface, that allows people with Litle & Co. merchant accounts to process Credit Card transactions.  An account with Litle is necessary to use this module.  Please talk to your representative before using this software.  In order to run the tests, you will need to get your test account setup (including access IP's) first.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Business::OnlinePayment::Litle

You can also look for information at:

